{
  "stem": "19690.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 214.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In [NON-ENGLISH] we got off the train and went to the Hotel de la Garde, directly across the street.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We got something to eat and then they took all of us-- there was 12 of us-- into a room upstairs.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they told us that we would be taken to Switzerland sometime within the next 24, hours just to rest.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had been on the train, it had been exciting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And naturally, in that kind of situation, you can't really sleep but we rested.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Around four o'clock she came back in, she divided us into two groups-- eight in one group, four in another.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The eight were-- I was one of the older ones, 13- 14-year-olds down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were supposed to go during the daytime.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The four older ones were joining an adult group that was going to be going at night through the mountains, a much more rigorous route.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Around 4:30, just before it got-- started to get dark, she took us with our luggage.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Our luggage was to stay behind, was coming later supposedly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we walked towards the cemetery area.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She had told us that what we would do, we would get to a big field and at the end of the field was a cemetery.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were going to pick dandelion, which is a salad delicacy in Europe in the spring, and put it in brown paper bags.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We each had our own brown paper bag.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then by her signal, which was going to be that she disappeared behind the wall of the cemetery, we are to make a beat for the border.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The border was on our right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a barbed wire double set about six feet high, crisscrossed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Beyond it was a river.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
